{"tid":1556551,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"沒普選即獨立, 若鎮壓即攬炒","createTime":"2019-09-09T18:54:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T19:56:41.000Z","uid":255402,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"adecb51bd6e872c49269392723a81ab013eb0552","tid":1556551,"uid":255402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T18:54:41.000Z","msg":"講比你聽中共<br />\n而家香港人經過三個月既反送中運動<br />\n已經鍊成左屬於我地香港人既國魂<br />\n亦代表緊參與過反送中既二百幾萬人入面<br />\n未來幾十年都唔會對中共有任何認同感<br />\n亦代表香港未來十幾二十年都唔可能有效統治<br />\n就算你捱得過呢次運動, 未來咁多單反港法例, 你以為香港人會就咁算?<br />\n<br />\n而家中共只係剩番兩條路, <br />\n一係比香港假獨立真自治, 大家投下投下投到獨立<br />\n一係鎮壓香港導致全球圍堵, 達至香港最終獨立<br />\n我係你習匪近平, 就諗清楚而家好做啲咩啦"},{"pid":"893cabf65faaffa19d651a30cb2e1ccf56bf8b3e","tid":1556551,"uid":214940,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T18:55:56.000Z","msg":"寧為飛灰<br />\n不作浮塵<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66bec28b9b7111273083d8895a5dfda10446ebae","tid":1556551,"uid":255402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T19:00:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55031145f2f59da0c692b9ab47f6a205aad1d234","tid":1556551,"uid":255402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T19:03:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3778815d3990a52f156c8e5d4f9770ce46fe77af","tid":1556551,"uid":31501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T19:05:38.000Z","msg":"寧為玉碎不作瓦全"},{"pid":"c7623f50c849efae1c272f594a8b8592ca69fd98","tid":1556551,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T19:08:16.000Z","msg":"不理性的熊類小動物要作出理性的選擇，牠會如何做決定呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cfdbffebafe27175bba674da4f3a053c37df921","tid":1556551,"uid":128102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T19:10:43.000Z","msg":"其實唔存在自治變獨立<br />\n因為基本法寫明要管國防同外交<br />\n普選會令香港脫離中國只不過係佢地唔想放棄高壓同既得利益"},{"pid":"3a5eaf7bada58b0f30884d3919338bc422344a96","tid":1556551,"uid":43204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T19:56:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}